The obscurity of Usenet providers' backbone relationships often results in users unknowingly purchasing multiple accounts on the same network.
This resource visually represents all major backbones and their associated resellers, showcasing retention levels.
Typically, one or two providers suffice for excellent retention and redundancy. Refer to the accompanying table and map legend for further details.
A small, passionate team constantly maintains and updates this map, published by rexum and accessible at usenet.rexum.space/tree.
It may not be 100% accurate, but we rely on the best available data and industry insights, please feel free to reach out to us.
